data.short_description: App crashes when trying to jump in search, when there exists a discord invite link around the message that hasn't been cached.
data.steps_to_repro: - Note: You can't post the link and try to search it since it would be in your cache. Try looking for an old message with the invite link. BUT, once you see the invite link, it gets cached, so you have to restart your app to clear it. - First, try searching something like "invite link"  - Tap some message that's not an actual invite link. (Jumping directly to the invite link works) - If there's an invite link around that message, it will crash.
